                  <additions>
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <desc type="Subscription"/>
                           <locus target="#83r"/>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">እምልደተ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ በ፲፻ወ፭፻ወ፩ዓመት፡ ተጽሕፈ፡ ወአሜሃ፡ ንጉሠ፡ ኢትዮጵያ፡ ናዖድ፡ ወልደ፡ እስክንድር፡ ኦርቶዶክሣዊ፡ ውእቱ
                              <q xml:lang="en"/>It is written in the year <date>1501</date>, when the king of Ethiopia was <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS7481NaodA">Nāʿod</persName>,
                              the son of <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS3874eskender">ʾƎskǝndǝr</persName> the Orthodox.</q>
                           <note>The date mentioned correspond to <date>1508 or 1509 CE.</date>,
                           but this is certainly not the date of the manuscript production.</note>

                        </item>
                     </list>
                  </additions>

